Bob: "It might be a worth a shot to do that and stand my ground on my next contract renewal time." Jen: "I will write him a strongly worded letter!" Bob: "Haha thank you for that!" Jen: "Hey we gotta get you some money somehow!" Prompt: A co-worker of mine got a promotion over me.

Jen: "Ugh I hate crap like that. Why can't credit be shared? Does it always have to be so cutthroat?" Bob: "Honestly, I'm indifferent as to how it's shared. Jen: "Hey people get what the deserve in this world sometimes. Just be glad justice is served." Bob: "For sure! I appreciate the support. Professionalism is tantamount."
